title: Campus Cup
overview: Which university or college has the best brains? In which field of study are the best students? Campus Cup wants to find an answer to that question. Campus Cup is a new prestigious student quiz by Canvas and Woestijnvis. The examiner on duty is Otto-Jan Ham. There is only one team from one course of study from one college or university that can win the ultimate TV exam on Canvas and be the winner of the Campus Cup for a year.
